original: Elfwing, Karl Vilhelm, civilingenjör, Göteborg, f. 12/3/04 i Karlskrona. G. 41 m. Ingrid Nilsson. Barn: Gunnel f. 42. — Avg:ex. fr. CTH 26. Res. t. Tyskl. 21-22, Tjecko.slov. 42-46. Anst. v. A-B Atlas-Diesel i Sthlm 28-31, A-B Hammarbyilampan 32, Örlogs-varvet i Karlskr. 33-36, Sv. Petrol. A-B Standard i Gbg 36-41, Boiinders Fabr. A-B i Gbg 41-42, h. Speoialfmiafölkiner A-B i Gbg fr. 42.
translated: Elfwing, Karl Vilhelm, engineer, Gothenburg, born March 12th, 1904 in Karlskrona. Married in 1941 to Ingrid Nilsson. Children: Gunnel born in 1942. Graduated from Chalmers University of Technology in 1926. Worked in Germany from 1921-1922, Czechoslovakia from 1942-1946. Employed at A-B Atlas-Diesel in Stockholm from 1928-1931, A-B Hammarbyilampan in 1932, Naval Shipyard in Karlskrona from 1933-1936, Swedish Petrol. A-B Standard in Gothenburg from 1936-1941, Boiinders Fabr. A-B in Gothenburg from 1941-1942, and as a specialist at fmiafölkiner A-B in Gothenburg from 1942 onwards.
